text: 나는 이것을 한국어로 쓰고 있는데, 당신이 그것을 읽을 수 있기를 바랍니다. 8개월 전만 해도 스트레이키즈가 누군지 몰랐는데 이제는 여러분에게 푹 빠져들고 있어요. 한씨가 이렇게 재능 있는 작사, 작곡, 래퍼인 줄 몰랐어요. 그리고 리? 우와. 보컬과 피치가 미쳤어요. Han's와 매우 매끄럽게 조화를 이룹니다. 이 트랙을 너무 좋아해요. 행복을 듣는 듯한 느낌. 이 곡을 만들어주신 두 분 모두 감사드립니다. 가능하다면 더 많은 노래를 함께 만들어주세요. 인도에서 많은 사랑을 받았습니다.

author: @todaywnowadays
text: I think antis don't understand how naive it is to think idols don't fall for their group members. Not only is it the entertainment industry, iykyk, but think about it: They are only around each other, allllll the time. They went through the phases of figuring what love is to them only around each other. Their family AND romantic love maps are centered solely around each other. They're constantly traveling together, performing together, receiving fan love together. Some will be friends/brothers, some will be more. Group members falling for each other has happened before, its happening now, and will keep happening. They're only human and we should ALWAYS be supportive.

author: @alisonfort8230
text:
Кажется, я стала зависимой от этой песни. Она такая теплая, весенняя, розовая, с запахом цветущей вишни и молодой травы. Её хочется слушать снова и снова, она как будто исцеляет душу и поднимает настроение. Она веселая и забавная, но текст такой серьезный, на самом деле. Конечно, всем любопытно, каким образом можно писать песню о любви и думать о Минхо😊😊😊Но что бы не происходило в голове у Хана тогда, он написал отличную песню о светлой и милой любви. 
Thank you, Han Jisung 🩷
Thank you, Lee Minho🩷
You are beautiful soulmates🩷 Please,  continue to get along well ❤️‍🩹🩷🫂

[리노 & 한 "Want so BAD" 가사]

[Verse 1: Lee Know]
문득 너를 사랑하게 돼서 (하게 돼서)
I think it's so sweet, my baby
아무 일도 손에 안 잡혔어
Oh, why?

It's a pretty big issue, why, 내 머릿속 수많은

With you everyday, sugar ride, 꽃밭이 잔뜩, my heart
나도 몰래 들어온 봄에 가슴 설레게 얼었다

몇 번이고 반복해서 재생 highlight

다가가지 절대 아닙니다 불장난
Let's get it started, 맘 타지 사리
분별 안 되지 주변 cosmos

나를 둘래 안아줄게 부는 게 바람이
었는지 설렘이셨는지

처음 본 순간부터 정해져 있었어
난 it's you (난 it's you, 난 it's you)
무의미한 신경전은 시간 아깝잖아 (아깝잖아)

author: @hoshithetigerboy
text:
another insight from this song was that LeeKnow’s voice is so tender, warm and sparkling(?) idk i just feel it that way. and only times (not really, but i can’t remember, i just woke up meh) i could hear LeeKnow’s genuine voice, his own expression, mood for the song was Want so BAD apparently and Limbo..? like solo stage for all members written/made by themselves or participating in making was a brilliant idea. 
we all know han jisung writes beautifully heartbreaking songs, 3rachas and hyunjin’s styles. but it was pretty new for me to listen to (+understand) minho, i.n, felix and seungmin’s. yk they never disappoint as you already know. so, Limbo was a new breath for me. i really love Minho’s voice.

author: @hoshithetigerboy
text:
when credits say lyrics by HAN and the whole song screams i was written by HAN…
idk there’s something special about songs Han wrote by himself. his lexicon is outstanding by the way..(idk which part, but when i was translating i read a line and it was SOOO JISUNG CODED, so i was like..yeah, man, you wrote this amazing song.

text: 오 민호샤, 당신의 생일이 다가왔습니다. 우리 고양이가 25살이 되었습니다! ❣️ 앞으로 당신에게 행복과 건강과 사랑이 가득하길 기원합니다. 수고해주셔서 감사합니다, 웃어주셔서 감사합니다, 멤버들과 스튜어디스 응원해주셔서 감사합니다, 저희 스테이, 많이 사랑합니다. 지난 5년간 여러분 모두 저희를 위해 애쓰셨습니다. 감사합니다. 리노님 저와 여러분 모두 정말 사랑한다는 점 잊지 마세요!!! 슬퍼하지 마십시오. 회원과 관리인이 있습니다. 우리는 항상 귀하를 지원할 준비가 되어 있습니다. 힘들면 모든 것을 혼자서만 이야기하지 마십시오. 당신은 너무 친절하고 아름답고 달콤하고 훌륭합니다   🏻 안돼요, 당신의 춤, 당신의 보컬, 당신의 랩이 나를 죽여요 💔 스테이는 당신에게 매우 애착을 갖고 있기 때문에 당신에 대한 사랑을 보여줍니다. 당신은 매우 긍정적입니다. 당신이 행복한 모습을 보는 것이 중요하다는 것을 기억하십시오. 행복해 행복해 스테이) 나 기분 안 좋을 때 바로 네 채널 들어가서 영상 보고 웃어줘 너의 미소가 날 웃게 만들어줘 <3 우리 새끼 고양이, 싫어하는 사람들 신경 쓰지 마세요, 부탁해요 너 (슬퍼하는 모습에 마음이 아프고 눈물이 난다 💔 웃는 게 너무 좋다는 말도 하고 싶다😭❤️ 너는 아름다워, 마침표. 사랑하는 사람들, 친구들, 멤버들, 나와 스티 사랑해 그리고 이민호 정말 고마워요  🏻  🏻😽

author: @hoshithetigerboy
text:
Another time of me watching, crying, commenting…It’s a cycle now.
I really want Jisung to know that! Like where I should send my thanks to Hanie? First of all, I really appreciate how Leeknow has more parts (i guess, don’t beat me if i’m wrong pls)…considering that Hanie wrote the lyrics, etc and still Lino has considerable amount of lines…(i mean, if i wrote the song i’d take the best and more parts for myself sorry ㅠㅠ i’m a bad person i guess)
Secondly, I really worship Hanie for letting us to hear Minho’s beautiful vocals..I really really appreciate his vocals..like i’ve listened to Limbo way too obsessively. I love how Minho sings. 
I love every kid’s vocals, they all can sing, that’s a fact. but for me i chose top-3, vocal king Kim Seungmin ofc, idk his voice has a soothing effect on me, our rock star Han Jisung, his voice makes me emotional, like it’s a therapy yk. and the last, but not least Lee Minho. He has that tender voice, i can’t fully explain, i’m so bad at this stuff, but what i want to say…there was a lack of Lino’s beautiful voice in ot8 discography of kids, not complaining, but yes! i’ve been fully satisfied only with unit songs, Limbo, etc. cuz wtf minho’s vocals, cmon, he’s not the bestest of the best, but at least, i need it for my mental stability. HAN JISUNG YOU ARE MY SAVIOR! THANK YOU A LOT. 

PS. when i was typing, just started “I worship” my ipad keyboard suggested me “Hanie” out of nowhere…i never used this expression before. that was kinda…scary? like is there someone inside my gadget? or is someone controlling my gadget without me knowing? nevermind.

author: @bgonjd
text:
Песня игривая, как пузыри шампанского ^_^
Мне вот интересно, как они это писали? Чан сказал скоро день музыки (а также  I Love Yarn Day=) давайте напишем что-нибудь праздничное, про любовь например, покосившись на минсонов. А что хороший подарок и любимых Стей (читай шиперов) порадовать. 
И они такие садятся на диванчик и решают -  надо прям слащаво слащаво - цветочки, радугу и солнышко, добавить розовенького.
Хан: "... цветы повсюду в моем сердце.."
а  Лино добавляет: 
- О-о-о и напиши  " весна пробралась в мое сердце". 
Занятно было бы посмотреть на это.  Наверно было весело писать эту песню. 

Хотя нет, написание песни видится мне в очень смущающей атмосфере. >_<

I LOVE MINSUNG SO SO SO MUCH 💙🤍

author: @my.Placebo.effect.325
text: *Stray Kids…. I’m going through so much right now, and I’m just scared. Anxiety, not feeling myself, I feel lost. My mood isn’t the same, I’m not myself. Heart racing, crying, feeling if I come in sight of anything, I will puke. I just can’t take it, not like I usually can. Today, I played your songs. I played them, I felt myself. I played Hero’s Soup. All of a sudden, everything bad was taken off my shoulders. I felt okay. I feel so. Freaking. Happy. It’s the little things. I notice you are all just humans like I. I realize everything you’ve all ever done, it was for your dreams and the dreams of many others. You guys were there to pick up millions of people. You do it every day. I don’t know where to begin. There is so much I have to say. My reasons why I love you all so much would go on like a Never Ending Story. I don’t usually use this account for anything other than BLACKPINK. I can’t use my other one; I’m too scared to be openly revealed to anyone. This is my secret account. I just come here to thank you. Such Beautiful people who inspire millions. I’m that one in a million. Thank you, Stray Kids. You will always be there. I can’t wait until I become someone just like all of you. You guys are my everything. You’re my everything and more. I love you guys, you make my heart happy, even when it was struggling physically and emotionally earlier. You always catch me, you save me so I can always be happy. Your existence simply in this world is what makes me feel this way. Your music does, too. You are all so special. Please never ever ever ever. Ever. Forget that. I love you, Stray Kids. I really, really love you. ♥️*

author: @kimsojun4282
text:
Straykids - such a big galaxy is mine.
I am a small planet in it, which is about to develop into pieces. There is no life in this small planet, only empty space. But because of you, this planet is blooming day after day, the life marks are already visible. I know you want to please your fans with all your might. But it’s enough for me to see your smiles on your face, it’s enough for me to hear your voices, and to see you healthy. This all makes me happy. I know I'm far from you. I can't attend your fan meeting. But I am always with you guys with all my heart. I will never lie, I love you as I love my loved ones. Move away the danger and be careful, please take care of yourself. I'm seriously worried about you guys. Because your concert is coming soon. Please take care of yourself again my angels. I love you with all my heart, and for the rest of my life. Thank you for being there in the kpop world.

author: @UniQAntiQ
text:
Alright it's been a day, and I've seen litte to nothing else than homophobia when it comes to this song.
Few things first, I understand you had no ill intentions, and you can't affect how fans react and act. I also hope you can understand this was merely what broke the camel's back. I'm speaking from experience that's been piling up for well over ten years, this song is in no way "the problem".
So, as A Gay myself, it is a tad disheartening to see the response this song has gotten. It's as if the mere thought of an idol being gay is the most vile, disgusting, disrespectful thing anyone could think of a person. As if being similar to us is vile. And we can't do anything, because there's nothing to stand on, because idols can't even date, let alone be not-straight. So nothing gets confirmed.
It's like Schrödinger's LGBTQ. You get to play with the idea and the support, without losing the homophobes. Homosexuality is so media sexy, until someone is actually gay.

I'm just baffled as to what went through y'all's heads in the publicing process of this song. There is no way, *no* way, I mean there's an absolute 0% chance, that you don't know about "MinSung". You could've made this a song for 3 people, could've added a lazy adlibbed "girl~" in there like is tradition in the industry. Or you could have stated that yes, this is a love song between the two people singing the song. But no, you did everything as you did, and released this. What were you expecting to happen? People not wondering if this is a coming out song? People not drawing any conclusions? Gay people ceasing to exist? I genuinely want to know what kind of reaction y'all wanted. Did you think it was funny?
Because right now, for a seasoned gay rat like myself, it's like I'm back in highschool, getting bullied, giggled at, and avoided. It's okay if straight girls kissed, but "gross" if lesbians had done it, and so on. People don't really want to be on this side, because then they'll get ostracized as well. And I get it.

This is the first time I've felt uncomfortable in this fandom, and I think that's why this whole thing struck so close to my soul. I just wish that "the higher ups", whoever they are who decide things like not allowing an idol to hold up a pride flag, I wish they are more thoughtful with this topic in the future, if possible. "Be for real" as they say. Stop playing both sides, please.


Anyway, I like this song so much. Thank you to Han and Lee Know for making it happen. I'm happy you're able to sing a happy song about love.

❤❤En un amor puro y verdadero,
Minho y Jisung, juntos, sinceros.

Dos almas unidas en una canción.

Descubriendo un amor sin engaño.

Jisung, con su risa tan rotunda.

Una conexión eterna y contenta.

Llenando de alegría su travesía.
Minho y Jisung, dos corazones valientes,
Enamorados y eternamente presentes.❤❤❤❤(cielo gabutti)

author: @not.you.not_me1285
text:
Hello guys! I want to thank you for this another grate masterpiece that you are offering us. I'm so happy and so hype out right now, and i feel like going crazy for all the love i feel for you! Just can't never have enough of you every day, even if i listen to you and your music every day, watching your content, Tik Tok's an Ig every day but feels like i never have enough! 
The song is just pure 🔥! 
Lee Know i am amazed... Your voice seems improved and more shifted song by song! You are doing such a wonderful job and i feel it's paying off the greate work that you are doing. 
HAN.... You are always my softiest spot... Whenever i see you or hear you i'm melting. You are so sweet, soft and powerful at the same time, and you never cease to impress me! Please! see this amazingness and wonderful and talented and sensible person that you are! Trust yourself and trust us.... cause ... You don't need to be perfect all the time! Stop pressuring yourself! We will still be here if you'll not feel like being to your top! 
Love you guys, love Skz, love all you are doing. 
Don't forget to take care of your self. I know that you are working even harder and this is the right time to prove even more because everyone is watching you and you have to make the difference but please don't forget that you need to rest and relax too. 
About the shipping of "Minsung" please don't be mad. We know that you are great friends for each other.... Is just that everyone loves love... 
Take good care of your self! 
Love and hugs from Romania for you and the other boys to! 
💙S͓̽t͓̽r͓̽a͓̽y͓̽K͓̽i͓̽d͓̽s͓̽💙 everywhere all around the world! 
Luv ya ❤! Luv ya ❤! Luv ya❤!

author: @Ross10969
text:
Sub Español “Want So Bad”
Me enamore de ti inesperadamente
Creo que eres demasiado dulce, cariño (o my baby)
Pero cuando estoy cerca tuyo, solo me quedo paralizado
Y me pregunto porque
Este problema da vueltas todo el dia en mi cabeza
Y me quedo despierto toda la noche pensando en como acercarme a ti
Porque cuando estoy contigo, todo se vuelve tan dulce
Y todo mi camino se llena de flores, cariño (o my heart) 
Se siente como si la primavera llegara de golpe
Y sorprendiera a mi corazon
Miremos el paisaje juntos
Como si estuvieramos en una escena de una pelicula
El amor es tan intuitivo
Hace que todo cambie
Esto es solo el comienzo de un típico romance
Aunque se cómo podría terminar esto, ya he caído
Perdidamente en ti, estoy muy ilusionado
…
Aunque esto sea algo muy cliche, me sigue emocionando
No estoy muy acostumbrado a todo esto, se que podria doler
Pero realmente lo quiero tanto
Oh si, dejemos el trailer de lado
Dejemos que la trama se desarrolle sola
Empecemos desde el inicio
Estamos de arriba a abajo, al igual que una montaña rusa
Acerquémonos un poco más
Juntos hacemos una película de comedia romántica
Pero cuidado, que con un error todo esto se podría terminar
Sigamos adelante, da un paso hacia mi
Acércate más que yo no estoy jugando
Empecemos de una vez, me estoy poniendo ansioso
No puedo pensar con claridad
Te regalaré un puñado de flores del cosmos,
Te amo, quiero permanecer a tu lado
Te abrazaré cuando el viento sople fuertemente
Todo lo que siento por ti va mucho mas alla del universo
He estado esperando este momento para poder decirte todo lo que siento
Si lo guardo por mas tiempo, podria explotar
(Se repite el estribillo…)
Desde la primera vez que te vi
Sabía que estábamos destinados a estar juntos
Para mi, solo existes tu
Sentirme nervioso ahora, es una pérdida de tiempo
Siempre has sido tu.
(Se repite el estribillo…)
❤❤❤❤❤

author: @hoshithetigerboy
text:
Beforehand apologies for this verbal diarrhea/. i’m just too emotional to that extent that i can steal chan’s laptop…regrets for later 

Okay guys. after listening to this beautiful song for the 1000 time…and scrolling my twt feed i couldn’t help but became delulu… oh that’s was a sweet venom…being (at least trying to be) normal, respective fan (STAY) then something like Want so BAD happens…and you lose your sanity. Being a delusional clown STAY is my full time job at this point. 

Dear, Jisung and Minho, don’t you dare explain yourself (oh dears you don’t have to…i’m just crying..sorry) like…idk…i lived 20 years and now one song made me asasasassasa? i can’t believe…i don’t want to believe in love other than minho and jisung have…like what was the purpose for those lyrics, hanie? i mean, if they dedicated to someone who’s name starts with li and end with no…then okay…ouh, my ceiling is not on place and my brain is not braining right now. thank you, good night mr. sleep late, but today sleep early. and mr. evil devil bunny, i record only with han jisung.

author: @serana_blossom
text:
그리고 스테이빌은 폭발했습니다!

SKZ, JYP 그리고 지구상의 모든 인간들이 민성호에 대해 알고 있습니다. 그들은 이 아름다운 노래를 공개 영역에 내놓았는데, 그 커버는 마치 사적인 순간에 찍은 것처럼 보입니다. 이 노래의 가사는 마치 서로에 대한 동경과 숭배, 그리고 사랑에 대한 상호 고백처럼 읽혔습니다. 이 노래가 암시하는 것이 무엇인지는 분명합니다. 만약 그것이 암시하는 것이 실제 현실에서 일어나지 않았다면, 단 1초도 이것이 SKZ 공식 채널에 공개되었을 것이라고 믿지 않습니다. 민성이 진짜인지를 고려해 볼 때, 글쎄 한씨가 가사를 쓰는 것은 좋은 시작입니다. 둘째, 가사는 서로에 대한 고백입니다 - 선택된 두 가수가 리노와 한씨라는 것을 알게 된 것에 대한 보너스로, 커버에 있는 '커플' 타입의 사진은 그것을 봉인합니다. 즉, 이것은 우리가 곧 경험할 수 있는 것처럼, 두 아이돌이 사랑하고 있다는 공개적인 고백입니다. 그리고 저는 그것에 대해 100% 만족합니다. 이 둘은 믿을 수 없을 정도로 함께 있고, 정말로 MFEO처럼 보이고, 서로를 완성시키는 것 같습니다 - 아마도 소울메이트의 전형이죠? 저는 아름다운 것들이 축하되어야 하고, 노래와 일어나고 있는 어떤 관계도 정말 아름답기 때문에 이로부터 반발이 없기를 바랍니다. 저는 지금 행복 이상입니다. 그들이 공공장소에서 큰 소리로 말하고, 그들의 관계를 소유하도록 허락된다면 저는 더 행복해질 수 있을 것입니다. Stray Kids는 종종 틀을 깨고 경계를 허물기 때문에, 아마도 이것은 그들이 과거의 쓰레기 같은 규칙에 굴복하지 않는 또 다른 예가 될 것입니다. 그렇기를 바랍니다!!!

author: @serana_blossom
text:
aaaaaaaaand then Stayville exploded!

🐇♥🐿♥🐇♥🐿♥🐇♥🐿♥🐇♥🐿♥🐇♥🐿♥🐇♥🐿♥🐇♥🐿♥🐇♥🐿♥🐇♥🐿

SKZ, JYP and ever human on the planet know about the Minsung ship. They've put this beautiful song out in the public domain, with a cover containing cute photos of Jisung and Minho, that very much look as though they were taken at private moments. The lyrics to this song read like a mutual confession of admiration and adoration, and of being in love. Its obvious what this song is implying.  I don't believe for a single second that this would have been released on the official SKZ channel, if what it implies was not happening in real life - that would be irresponsible and problematic. In considering whether Minsung is real, well Han writing the lyrics is a good start. Second, the lyrics are mutual confessions - that the two chosen singers being Lino and Han adds a huge weight. As a confirmation bonus, the 'couple' type photos on the cover seal it.  So, in a nutshell, this is as open a confession of two idols being in love, as I believe we'll experience any time soon - and I'm 100% here for it.  These two are incredible together and truly seem MFEO, its like they complete each other - the epitome of soulmates, perhaps? I hope that there is no backlash from this because beautiful things should be celebrated - and the song, and any relationship that is happening, are indeed, beautiful.  I am beyond happy right now.  I could only be happier if they were allowed to say it out loud in public and own their relationship. Stray Kids often break molds and push boundaries, so perhaps this is going to be another example of them not bowing down to the rubbish rules of the past. Hope so!!!
🐇♥🐿♥🐇♥🐿♥🐇♥🐿♥🐇♥🐿♥🐇♥🐿♥🐇♥🐿♥🐇♥🐿♥🐇♥🐿♥

author: @hoshithetigerboy
text:
I only wish Jisung was happy. It’s so great to hear a romantic song, but with light vibe and heartwarming lyrics. I appreciate all Jisung’s recordings, and i can reflect myself on them, but song about happy, mutual love makes me even happier. In order to write/produce song, genuine, sincere music you have to undergo the same feelings/emotions…it all comes out from the heart. and seeing, to be precise, listening to this amazing, light, bright, beautiful song…I’m more than happy. Can’t wait to see other common projects of Hanie with his Lino hyung. Their voices really match well. 

Han is actually genius. How can he come up with such a deep message through words, he finds some unexpected, complicated concepts i’ve never heard before. cosmos flowers? i’m pretty sure stays bombarding search bars with this inquiry… there are lots of interesting things…i’ll find out more later. 

my whole twt and IG feed just going crazy over this release. it’s so funny…

so, 이민호씨 한지성씨… 승민씨 말대로 결혼하셨어요? Ah, not to be weird, but is this song your firstborn (sorry for my pathetic humor)

Don't get me started with the vocals and rapping, omg they are just so beautiful!!! Jisung being insane for his singing AND rapping. Can't get over that honestly. What an ace he is! The lyrics got me blushing, smiling, and fangirling so hard, I love my Minsung so much 😭🥹 Anyways, I'm gonna be putting this song on repeat now because I'm too in love ahhhh so happy Minsung finally sang a song together!!!! So proud of them! Hope to see them continue singing more together ahhh this is an amazing first song. Thank you for this happy, beautiful, and heart-fluttering song, Minsung 🥹 Luv you guys so much!!!! 🥰❤️
